 ============================================================
 = Internet Watcher     --    Hack to fix iMacs WIFI issues =
 ============================================================

== DESCRIPTION ==
An AppleScript to watch your Internet connection and restart Airport when the Internet connection is lost.

== INSTRUCTIONS ==
You will have to edit the script file to add your admin login and password. Look for the lines to uncomment and edit towards the end of the code.

